-- Batista Says May Sell EBX Stake to Industrial Group
-- B y   J u a n   P a b l o   S p i n e t t o
-- 2012-04-30T17:53:55Z
-- http://www.bloomberg.com/news/2012-04-30/batista-says-may-sell-ebx-stake-to-industrial-group.html
 Billionaire Eike Batista said he
may sell a stake in his holding company EBX Group Co. to an
industrial group.  Batista said he is considering to sell a stake in EBX to
have an “extra stamp” of approval from investors, he said
during an interview on Bloomberg Television’s “Money Moves”
today.  To contact the reporter on this story:
